author: niclas
msg: Applying patch from Cameron Fieber. This patch fixes a bug where the ModelMBeanInfo would fail to build for indexed type properties (by basically ignoring them for now, eventually it will treat them as operations), as well as supporting more information on introspected operations if it is available.
